profile:
Austin Tool Rentals Ltd is the lower mainland's leading tool rental company.

The driving force behind our reputation are our employees, who work tirelessly to be your neighbourhood tool rental company.   

Throughout our 30 years in business,  Austin Tool Rentals Ltd has been known for our commitment to building long-lasting relationships with our clients and our community. We take pride in our dedication to excellence, our reputation for quality, and our commitment to having the right tool to get the job done right.  Our clients appreciate our emphasis on value, quality, sustainability and efficiency.

At the heart of our business, passion continues to drive us forward. Today, the Austin Rentals Ltd name has grown to be synonymous with uncompromising quality and outstanding service in your neighbourhood.

Next time you have a job to do, we have the tools to get the job done right.  Please contact us and ask how we can help.
